    Conditions of Use
    The user may use, distribute, and modify the licensed work only if they comply with the following conditions:

    Attribution: The user must give appropriate credit to the author, provide a link to the license, and indicate if changes were made.
    Non-Commercial Use: The user may not use the licensed work for commercial purposes without the prior written consent of the author.
    Share Alike: If the user modifies the licensed work, they must distribute their work under the same license as the original.

    Term and Termination
    This license is effective until terminated by either party. The author may terminate this license at any time if the user fails to comply with any of the terms and conditions of this FUSL. Upon termination, the user must immediately cease using, distributing, and modifying the licensed work.

